document_data.name: the Sixfold Symmetry
document_data.mainbody: The '''Sixfold Symmetry''' was a mercenary organization within the [[Sevenfold Mazework]] of the [[Great Dismal Delve]].
document_data.Organization: The Sixfold Symmetry was made-up of 500 [[crysmal]] mercenaries.
document_data.Activities: The activities of this group was unknown, but they were never seen outside of the Sevenfold Mazework.
document_data.Base of Operations: The Sevenfold Mazework within the Great Dismal Delve served as base of all dao military organizations.
